Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.07,0:00:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem. Morning, Sunburst.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.37,0:00:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Oh. Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.27,0:00:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.39,0:00:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, no matter how\Nmany times I read it,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.50,0:00:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Houyhnhnm's Guide to Magical\NArcana never gets boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.81,0:00:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.12,0:00:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got another letter\Nfor you from Sires Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.35,0:00:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm. Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.44,0:01:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.44,0:01:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I be experiencing the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.67,0:01:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Cerebration Transmogrification\NEffect described in Chapter 17?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.75,0:01:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my cutie mark is glowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.75,0:01:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,My cutie mark is glowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.65,0:01:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what this means!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.32,0:01:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I yelling!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.70,0:02:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Twilight,\Nwhat an honor this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.47,0:02:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.77,0:02:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm called for a\Nfriendship mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.21,0:02:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.32,0:02:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And it must be\Na special one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.03,0:02:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Nopony outside of Ponyville\Nhas ever been called before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.05,0:02:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If you need some\Npointers, let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.85,0:02:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been on my fair\Nshare of missions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.05,0:02:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been on\None, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.52,0:02:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's.. my\Nfair share.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.66,0:02:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.78,0:02:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean we've\Nboth been called?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.00,0:02:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[unexcited]\NYeah. Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you excited?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.64,0:02:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You and me!\NOn a mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.97,0:02:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry, are you not excited\Nto go on a mission with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.48,0:02:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.08,0:02:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I mean, yes. Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.85,0:03:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Totally excited about\Nus going together,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,just not so excited\Nabout where.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sires Hollow?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.72,0:03:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. Home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.79,0:03:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.73,0:03:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I can go if\Nyou two don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.20,0:03:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I am kind of an expert.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.42,0:03:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that I don't\Nwant to go home,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.45,0:03:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just that whenever I do,\Nmy dad treats me like a filly,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.19,0:03:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,like nothing's changed\Nsince I was a foal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.43,0:03:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.13,0:03:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. I'm a horrible\Ndaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.90,0:03:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.13,0:03:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My mom actually does\Nkind of the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.20,0:03:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.28,0:03:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even have to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.97,0:03:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She sends me\Nletters constantly
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.64,0:03:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,asking about my plans\Nfor the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.67,0:04:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"You're a grown-up pony,{\i0}\N{\i1}Sunburst. You need a plan."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.54,0:04:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't been home\Nin a while either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.88,0:04:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. We'll just have to\Nexplain to our parents
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.58,0:04:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,that we're on an important\Nfriendship mission,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.45,0:04:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,so they can't bother us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.19,0:04:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think\Nthat will work?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.66,0:04:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.33,0:04:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[sigh] The great\Nthing about home is
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.87,0:04:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,it always stays\Njust how you left--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.14,0:04:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[bang] OH!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.24,0:04:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did that come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.35,0:04:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[woman's voice over speaker]\NWelcome to Sires Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Essence?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.49,0:04:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Essence of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.09,0:04:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.09,0:04:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.29,0:04:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. Chocolate? Maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.13,0:04:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Not chocolate maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.83,0:04:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Chocolate definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.70,0:05:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And all of the benefits\Nwith none of the drawbacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.01,0:05:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't this used to\Nbe a fruit stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what\Nit used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.21,0:05:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sires Hollow Development\NCommittee determined what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sires Hollow\NDevelopment what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.55,0:05:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do ponies buy fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.18,0:05:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You can get a fruit\Nsmoothie two doors down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.82,0:05:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All the shops are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Not everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the same as it ever was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, our bookstore's\Nbeen declared a
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.38,0:05:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,"site of historical\Nsignificance"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.88,0:05:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,by the Sires Hollow\NPreservation Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.62,0:05:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to experience\Nthe books from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.22,0:05:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why windows\Nare see-through.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.43,0:05:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.73,0:06:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Preservation Society?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.56,0:06:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What is happening around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.20,0:06:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll explain it to\Nyou, Sugar-Plum.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.83,0:06:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You are just as\Ncutsie-wootsie as ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.07,0:06:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.58,0:06:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Just a father wanting to\Npreserve our town's rich history
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.38,0:06:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,for his little\NPumpkie-Wumpkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad. You promised no\Npumpkie-wumpkins in public.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.95,0:06:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[whispers]\NSorry, Chipmunk Cheeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Er. Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.89,0:06:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're preserving\Nthe whole town?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.46,0:06:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.51,0:06:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's exactly\Nwhat I told him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.26,0:06:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, "Firelight,\Nyou're crazy."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.97,0:06:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.99,0:06:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Our village needs the\Nsame thing you do, Sunburst:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.81,0:06:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,a clear plan\Nfor the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.94,0:06:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I started the Sires\NHollow Development Committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.11,0:06:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've got plans\Nfor this little town.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.02,0:06:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Big plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.30,0:07:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen here, Stellar Flare; I'm\Nnot going to let you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.92,0:07:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,turn our historical heritage\Ninto Las Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.66,0:07:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm not going to let\Nyou turn it into a museum!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.76,0:07:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you two fighting over this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, having a\Nfriendship problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.54,0:07:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.07,0:07:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Because there is\Nno friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the good news is\Nwe know why we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.71,0:07:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should have\Nsent Spike after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.57,0:07:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunburst and I were\Ncalled here to do a job
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.97,0:07:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and it looks like\Nyou two are it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.14,0:07:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean your success\Ndepends on us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.21,0:07:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.23,0:07:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And you have to hang out with\Nus the whole time you're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.25,0:08:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.35,0:08:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll hear what\Nyou have to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.65,0:08:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,but every plan I've\Nmade for this town
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.35,0:08:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,is perfectly reasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck convincing me\Nmy preservation efforts
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,don't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.46,0:08:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[voiceover]\NWelcome to Sires Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.27,0:08:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So we can't hold the books?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.87,0:08:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha ha ha ha. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.54,0:08:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Can{\i1} you {\i0} hold the books?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.08,0:08:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So nopony can\Nread the books?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.35,0:08:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckle] Isn't she adorable?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.43,0:08:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[voiceover]\NWelcome to Sires Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You can call them... smells,\Nbut I call them essence!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.11,0:09:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Fruity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.71,0:09:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad there's nowhere\Nto get actual fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.65,0:09:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,In the future, all ponies\Nwill drink their fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.31,0:09:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,One hundred percent\Nancient pony grains.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.13,0:09:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like the town\Nfounders ate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.93,0:09:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hope you like crust!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.07,0:09:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[squeak]\NWelcome to Sires Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Sires Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.91,0:09:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Sires Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.98,0:09:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Sires Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.31,0:09:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Sires--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.33,0:09:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, it's annoying. I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.29,0:09:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe my preservation efforts\Nwere a little over the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.29,0:09:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...\NOh no.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.36,0:09:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And I might have been\Ntrying to turn the town
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.46,0:09:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,into a shopping mall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.30,0:09:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever direction\Nthe town takes, from now on
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.13,0:10:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,how about we work\Ntogether on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.43,0:10:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.47,0:10:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunburst, you should\Nmove closer to Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.44,0:10:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,After this success, I'm sure\Nthe Princess of Friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.31,0:10:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,will want to send you\Non more missions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not really\Nhow it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, look at the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.65,0:10:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We should get going,\Nnow that we've solved
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.39,0:10:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the friendship problem!\NRight, Starlight?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.32,0:10:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. The thing is, I don't\Nthink we did solve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.03,0:10:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,When we solve a\Nfriendship problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.49,0:10:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,our cutie marks are\Nsupposed to glow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww, don't be\Ndisappointed, Puddin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Your papa will work\Nthis out for ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[sigh] My papa wasn't called by the\Nmap in Twilight's castle; I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you going to explain\Nthis to the princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.65,0:10:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your plan if she fires\Nyou from friendship quests?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.28,0:10:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.03,0:10:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.97,0:10:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.02,0:10:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Use your words, Sunburst.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.16,0:10:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you two\Nweren't the problem
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.66,0:11:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,we were sent to\Nsolve, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.83,0:11:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So now you don't even\Nknow why you're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to figure this out\Nbefore we run out of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.80,0:11:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[sigh] Mom. There\Nisn't a time limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.50,0:11:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're here for\Nan extra-long visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.09,0:11:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You can stay in your\Nold room, Punkie-Wunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like you left it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.02,0:11:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[softly] We need to find this\Nfriendship problem... now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.42,0:11:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I know you have\Nyour little job to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,but Stellar and I know the\Ntown a lot better than you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.11,0:11:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither of you have\Nbeen home in ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.53,0:11:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to need\Nour help to succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.37,0:11:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that\Nmakes sense...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I already have\Nsome ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.04,0:11:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I liked it better\Nwhen they were fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.95,0:11:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.38,0:12:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I've explained how\NSires Hollow was founded,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.42,0:12:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,we can start to explore all the\Npossible friendship problems
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that might have\Ndeveloped over time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.36,0:12:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate the\Nhistory lesson, Dad,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.90,0:12:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but I need to find\Nthe problem now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.53,0:12:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,in the present.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.47,0:12:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, now Hon-Bun, how\Nare you gonna do that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.60,0:12:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,without all the\Nbackstory, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.74,0:12:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, of course I know\Nhow hard it is for you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.41,0:12:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to sit still and focus, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.21,0:12:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Would it help you pay attention\Nto hold on to your bwankie?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.32,0:12:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you've had a little\Nsetback, but don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.33,0:12:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I know exactly what\Nyou need to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.66,0:12:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Make a plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Already got one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.00,0:12:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Step one: interview\Nthe suspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.20,0:12:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Step two: use your talents\Nto solve the issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.27,0:12:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Step three: get the\NPrincess of Friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.47,0:12:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to send you on\Nmore missions!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.51,0:12:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom! IT DOES NOT\NWORK LIKE THAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.85,0:12:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,AHEM.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.62,0:13:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[acting]\NOh, thank goodness you are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.29,0:13:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,These two ponies refuse\Nto use my essences.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.93,0:13:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe because we don't like\Nto cover our natural scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.87,0:13:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,AHEM!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.51,0:13:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And {\i1}she{\i0} refuses\Nto buy our books.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.78,0:13:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[all together]\NSurely this is a\Nfriendship problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.59,0:13:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It needs to be a real\Nfriendship problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.49,0:13:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just make one up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.06,0:13:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,URGH!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.79,0:13:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what happens\Nwhen we don't rehearse!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.33,0:13:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,UGH.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.00,0:13:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.23,0:13:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweetie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.20,0:13:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I found a really old town\Nbylaw that nopony agrees on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.67,0:14:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, we're not\Nsupposed to prance
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,or canter after dinnertime.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.18,0:14:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Could that be the problem?\NSillyfilly?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.98,0:14:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.79,0:14:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[sigh] Hiding from my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.89,0:14:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She started making up friendship\Nproblems for me to solve.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.26,0:14:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.. My dad won't even let\Nme talk to anypony,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.33,0:14:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,in case they're "strangers."\NI'm A GROWN MARE!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.62,0:14:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We're never going to find\Nthe friendship problem
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.60,0:14:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,with them around,\Nlet alone solve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.14,0:14:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you two should start\Nlooking for it on your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, so we wanted to talk to all\Nof you, you know, in private.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.72,0:14:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Just to see if there were\Nissues any of you had
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.85,0:14:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,with your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.69,0:14:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.79,0:14:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one question.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.59,0:14:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are we whispering?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.76,0:14:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They're avoiding their parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.73,0:14:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.87,0:15:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Not avoiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.44,0:15:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Just.. taking a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.31,0:15:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.24,0:15:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We needed to focus, but we're\Ndefinitely not avoiding them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.01,0:15:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're whispering\Nwith all of us
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.25,0:15:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,in the darkest corner\Nof the shop,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.05,0:15:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,where nopony can\Npossibly see
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.12,0:15:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,because you're\N{\i1}not{\i0} avoiding them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.92,0:15:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.59,0:15:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Er.. but they definitely can't\Nhear us in here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.36,0:15:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.39,0:15:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the\Nantiquities section.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.23,0:15:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Nopony ever comes\Nback here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.16,0:15:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Firelight: There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.03,0:15:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But what are you doing in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] Is the\Nfriendship problem
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.44,0:15:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,in my favorite section\Nof the book store?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.35,0:15:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...and then I\Nthought the best way
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to look for a friendship\Nproblem in the present...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.42,0:15:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.27,0:15:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...was to look back in our\Ntown history even farther!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.09,0:15:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Stellar Flare: Sunburst!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.56,0:15:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Finally.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.03,0:16:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I know you don't want\Nme to "make up" a problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.30,0:16:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but what if I START one?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.03,0:16:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not how this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.50,0:16:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, no pony ever became\Na success by following
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.17,0:16:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,all the rules, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.44,0:16:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How are things\Non your end?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.94,0:16:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't be better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,New leads and such!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.11,0:16:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.18,0:16:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We really are providing\Nexcellent assistance, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.55,0:16:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.53,0:16:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I dare say our children should\Nbe grateful for our help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.52,0:16:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,GUYS!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.09,0:16:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Both: We don't WANT your HELP!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, you\Ndon't want our help?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.14,0:16:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[laugh] That's--that's\Nridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.74,0:16:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What reason could you\Npossibly have for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.87,0:16:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,BECAUSE YOU'RE DRIVING US CRAZY!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.54,0:16:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.68,0:16:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And just how am I\Ndriving you crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.75,0:16:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,By always coming up with plans!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.08,0:17:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need a plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.15,0:17:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, maybe I do, but\Nit'll be mine, not yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.76,0:17:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sorry\Nfor trying to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.40,0:17:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're not any better.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.40,0:17:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a filly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.27,0:17:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a grown pony with a job to\Ndo and I'll do it on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.34,0:17:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll let you\Nget to it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.68,0:17:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Great...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.72,0:17:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we have to smooth things\Nover with our parents
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.95,0:17:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,on top of finding and solving\Na friendship problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost like our\Nrelationship with our parents
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.36,0:17:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,is the friendship problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.06,0:17:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think\Nthat's it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.23,0:17:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.63,0:17:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what all\Nof us think.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.20,0:17:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.05,0:17:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why couldn't we have been sent\Nto stop a war or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.24,0:17:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.85,0:18:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Ms. Glimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.25,0:18:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How is your friendship\Nproblem search going?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I only ask as an\Ninterested observer,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.45,0:18:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,since I know you are an\Nadult who's capable
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.59,0:18:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,of doing things without\Nhelp from anypony else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.66,0:18:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I think Sunburst\Nand I figured out what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.06,0:18:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Stellar and I weren't\Nreally helpful after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.23,0:18:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we haven't\Nactually solved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't think we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.94,0:18:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Not without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.98,0:18:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Pungent!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.32,0:18:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, did you come by\Nto be driven crazy
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.26,0:18:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,by more of your mother's plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.19,0:18:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I came to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's going to take\Nmore than an apology
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.00,0:18:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,to make up for telling me\Nyou don't want my help
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.50,0:18:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,finding your friendship problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.77,0:18:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm not sorry for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.34,0:18:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight and I already figured\Nout what the problem is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.21,0:19:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a terrible apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.24,0:19:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you come with\Nme and help fix it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.75,0:19:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a better one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.02,0:19:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually, Twilight or one of\Nour other friends gets called
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.69,0:19:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to a place with a\Nfriendship problem to fix.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.62,0:19:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But Starlight and I\Nrealized we came here
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,to fix a friendship\Nproblem we already had.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.99,0:19:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I've been\Navoiding coming home, Dad,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.76,0:19:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but you can't keep\Ntreating me like a foal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.37,0:19:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Sugarbun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.97,0:19:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I just know how hard things\Nwere for you when you left home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I wanted you to feel\Nsafe, like when you were young.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.85,0:19:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, I know I've\Nmade some mistakes,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.88,0:19:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll probably\Nmake a bunch more,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.02,0:19:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,but I learn from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.75,0:19:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's\Nwhat growing up is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.49,0:19:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I never told you how\Nmuch your plans bothered me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.66,0:19:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and I know you just\Nwant me to succeed,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.16,0:19:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but I need to do\Nthat on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.47,0:20:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember how\Nlost you were
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.10,0:20:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,when you flunked out\Nof magic school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.94,0:20:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought as long\Nas you had a plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.11,0:20:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd never feel\Nthat way again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.34,0:20:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.88,0:20:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to find my own way,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.71,0:20:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,but I definitely don't\Nfeel lost anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.69,0:20:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.00,0:20:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The glowing cutie mark is such\Na symbol of accomplishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.97,0:20:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't suppose\Nthere's a way for you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.64,0:20:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,to get it to glow all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.31,0:20:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh heh. Pretty sure it\Ndoesn't work that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Not unless we solved a\Nfriendship problem every few
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.11,0:20:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,seconds, and I kinda hope this\None will be it for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.65,0:20:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it seems to me your\Nmap is saying we're not just
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,your parents; we're\Nyour friends too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.46,0:20:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.19,0:21:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if I promise to treat you\Nless like a little filly
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.53,0:21:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and more like a friend,\Nwill you visit more?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.93,0:21:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.00,0:21:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you start to\Ndrive me crazy again,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.47,0:21:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you instead\Nof never coming home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.47,0:21:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's lovely of you to\Nsay, dear, but you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.14,0:21:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I can always visit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.48,0:21:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Stellar, you're a genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.31,0:21:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.45,0:21:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you feel\Nabout a road trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.58,0:21:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I might have a few\Nplans for that.
